				<h1 class="shead-style text-center">HARYANA</h1>
				<p>A historical land it has always been associated with various kingdoms and regions, officially given its status by language distinction. Over the years it has changed its shape and structure due to its position. Home to the ancient Indus valley civilization many of the ancient sites, canals; rain water harvestment systems have been uncovered from this land. </p><p>
        Rebuilt and destroyed many times during history it has stood for many years witnessing historic battles and incidents. The modern day Haryana has many of the ancient ruins and scriptures from many different dynasties and kingdoms. Today state sponsored tourism development acts have attracted many visitors and travelers to witness the history some of what is forgotten and lost.
        </p>
